==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ungowned
<hw>Un*gowned"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <ety>[1st
pref. <ets>un-</ets> + <ets>gown</ets>.]</ety> <def>Stripped of a gown;
unfrocked.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <ety>[Pref. <ets>un-</ets> not +
<ets>gowned</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not having, or not wearing, a
gown.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ungraceful</ent>⟦br⟧
